    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine requires significant repair as it currently struggles to idle and exhibits a noticeable knock, while the transmission slips during gear changes. Externally, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will require a tow and substantial mechanical work to be roadworthy again.",
