    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, stone chips, or swirls, recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in absolute pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original floor mats are spotless. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the touchscreen interface, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete service history from authorized dealerships and incredibly low mileage. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage reflects the vehicle's pampered life. This is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier example that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. All original keys, manuals, and service records are included.",
      "price": 46500.0,
